section.div: This project explores the use of SPY pricing data and sentiment data feed from Social Market Analytics to generate a one-day SPY forecast. In order to create accurate forecast we are utilizing SMA S-Factors, minute-wise activity feed and price data to predict one-day SPY Close to Close price.
using the Inverse-Transform method to speed up options pricing simulations in R
A high-frequency trading model using Interactive Brokers API with pairs and mean-reversion in Python
